title: Analysis: Princes Andrew and Harry will keep their last royal roles. But there's a catch
description: When King Charles III celebrated his birthday earlier this week, the headlines focused on the new monarch taking on a new park ranger post previously held by his father, Prince Philip.

title: What is Bud Zero, the only beer Budweiser can sell at the World Cup?
description: In a surprise reversal, Qatar announced a ban of alcoholic beer at the eight stadiums hosting the World Cup. That leaves fans with just one "beer" choice — albeit one that isn't boozy.

title: Fed officials crushed investors' hopes this week
description: Investors sleuthing for clues about what the Federal Reserve will decide during its December policy meeting got quite a few this week. But those hints about the future of monetary policy point to an outcome they won't be very happy about.

title: Asia must not become arena for 'big power contest,' says China's Xi as APEC summit gets underway
description: Chinese leader Xi Jinping has stressed the need to reject confrontation in Asia, warning against the risk of cold war tensions, as leaders gather for the last of three world summits hosted in the region this month.

title: Global investors are bullish again on China as Beijing switches to damage control
description: Market sentiment on Chinese stocks hit rock bottom just weeks ago after President Xi Jinping secured a historic third term in power and stacked his top team with loyalists in a clean sweep not seen since the Mao era.

title: Inside Twitter as 'mass exodus' of staffers throws platform's future into uncertainty
description: Death is in the air on Twitter.

title: Latin Grammys 2022: See who won
description: The 23rd Latin Grammy Awards are taking place on Thursday.
